<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِّمَّا أُوتُوا}</span> ... مِمَّا أُعْطُوا مِنْ مَالِ الفَيْءِ وَغَيْرِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَصَاصَةٌ}</span> ... حَاجَةٌ، وَفَقْرٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُوقَ}</span> ... يُكْفَ وَيُجَنَّبْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شُحَّ نَفْسِهِ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> الشُّحُّ:</span> بُخْلٌ بِالمَالِ مَعَ حِرْصٍ عَلَيْهِ، وَتَطَلُّعٍ لِمَا بِيَدِ غَيْرِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
